<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>주문 완료</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/order-complete.css" />
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <main class="container page">
            <section class="complete-box">
                <div class="complete-icon">✓</div>
                <p class="complete-label">ORDER COMPLETE</p>
                <h2 class="complete-title">주문이 완료되었습니다</h2>
                <p class="complete-desc">
                    결제가 정상적으로 완료되었습니다.<br />
                    아래 버튼을 눌러 구매한 상품을 확인하거나 다운로드할 수 있습니다.
                </p>

                <div class="complete-info" id="complete-info-box">
                    <div class="complete-info-row">
                        <span>주문번호</span>
                        <strong>-</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="complete-info-row">
                        <span>결제금액</span>
                        <strong>-</strong>
                    </div>
                    <div class="complete-info-row">
                        <span>상품명</span>
                        <strong>-</strong>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="complete-actions">
                    <a href="/mypage-page" class="btn btn-primary">내 구매상품 보기</a>
                    <a href="/products-page" class="btn btn-outline">상품리스트로 이동</a>
                </div>
            </section>
        </main>
        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
            <script src="/js/order-complete.js"></script>
            <script src="/js/common.js"></script>
</body>

</html>